<section class="store-sections" aria-label="Future store sections">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Store layout</p>
    <h2>More store sections are ready, but intentionally empty.</h2>
    <p>
      These blocks are placeholders for real future activity. They add structure without inventing
      products, prices, testimonials, or performance numbers.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="empty-section">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Top Sells</p>
      <h3>Top sells will appear after launch.</h3>
      <p>Reserved for real store data once Guidora has active digital releases and verified performance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="placeholder-grid six" aria-hidden="true">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </div>
    <span class="lock">Coming Soon</span>
  </div>

  <div class="empty-section">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">New Arrivals</p>
      <h3>New digital releases will be listed here.</h3>
      <p>This area is prepared for future launches and remains empty until real resources are added.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="placeholder-grid six" aria-hidden="true">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </div>
    <span class="lock">Coming Soon</span>
  </div>

  <div class="empty-section">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Reviews</p>
      <h3>Verified reviews are coming later.</h3>
      <p>Customer feedback will be shown only after real purchases or verified product experiences exist.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="placeholder-grid" aria-hidden="true">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </div>
    <span class="lock">Coming Soon</span>
  </div>

  <div class="empty-section">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Launch Updates</p>
      <h3>Store updates will be posted here.</h3>
      <p>Future announcements, release notes, and launch windows can be placed in this area.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="placeholder-grid" aria-hidden="true">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </div>
    <span class="lock">Coming Soon</span>
  </div>

  <div class="waitlist-panel">
    <p class="eyebrow">Updates</p>
    <h2>Join before the store opens.</h2>
    <p>Get notified when Guidora publishes its first official digital releases.</p>
    <a class="button" href="/pages/contact">Join Waitlist</a>
  </div>
</section>

